<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/51db22a717.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alata&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-container">
        <div class="login-form-container shadow">
            <div class="login-form-right-side">
                <div class="top-logo-wrap">
                </div>
                <h1>PetClinic Doctor Page</h1>
                <p style="color: black">PetClinic 웹/앱의 수의사 전용 페이지로 화상 통화, 고객 관리, 회원 정보 수정, 병원 등록 등 다양한 기능을 활용할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="login-form-left-side">
                <div class="login-top-wrap">
                    <span>Don't have an account?</span>
                    <button class="create-account-btn" onClick="location.href='/auth/signup'">Create Profile</button>
                </div>
            <form action="/auth/detail" method="post">
                <div class="login-input-container">
                    <div class="login-input-wrap input-id">
                        <i class="far fa-envelope" style="color:#AFD485;"></i>
                        <input placeholder="Email" type="text" name="email" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="login-input-wrap input-password">
                        <i class="fas fa-key" style="color:#AFD485;"></i>
                        <input placeholder="Password" type="password" name="password" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="login-btn-wrap">
                    <button class="login-btn" type="submit">Login</button>
                </div>
            </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>